== 历史 ==
XVideos是一个色情影片分享网站，它是一个类似于[[YouTube|YouTube]]为一般用户提供类似[[RedTube|RedTube]]成人内容的影片网站，內容来自专业色情影片業者（有时是盗版）的影片片段，以及业余色情影片制作者。[[法比安·蒂曼|法比安·蒂曼]]([[MindGeek|MindGeek]]之所有者)试图於2012年收购XVideos以壟斷色情网站，而XVideos的法籍業主拒绝了超过1.2亿美元的报价，他说：“对不起，我必须去玩暗黑破坏神II。”<ref name="Economist">{{Cite news |date=September 26, 2015 |title=Naked capitalism |work=The Economist |url=https://www.economist.com/news/international/21666114-internet-blew-porn-industrys-business-model-apart-its-response-holds-lessons |access-date=August 31, 2017 |archive-date=2018-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212072524/https://www.economist.com/news/international/21666114-internet-blew-porn-industrys-business-model-apart-its-response-holds-lessons }}</ref> 2014年，XVideos企图强迫内容提供者承诺放弃从账户中删除影片或立即关闭其账户的权利而引发争议。<ref name="avn1">{{Cite magazine |date=August 13, 2014 |title=XVideos.com Tube Site Accused of Strong-Arming Uploaders |url=https://avn.com/business/articles/technology/xvideos-com-tube-site-accused-of-strong-arming-uploaders-569826.html |magazine=AVN |access-date=August 31, 2017 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142630/https://avn.com/business/articles/technology/xvideos-com-tube-site-accused-of-strong-arming-uploaders-569826.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Online porn websites promote 'sexually violent' videos |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-56640178 |website=BBC News |access-date=25 April 2021 |date=5 April 2021 |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408101925/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-56640178 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/16/opinion/sunday/companies-online-rape-videos.html|title=Why Do We Let Corporations Profit From Rape Vidoes ?|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220510195006/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/16/opinion/sunday/companies-online-rape-videos.html}}</ref>

